{"tid":766267,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）荃灣斬人案兩傷　其中一人胸口受傷　與輕傷者分送兩醫院","createTime":"2018-08-03T12:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T14:21:48.000Z","uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16956b997a5836e5ba899bcae020ed82d590fc19","tid":766267,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一片段，顯示一名男子疑胸口受傷坐在地上，由友人協助止血。上傳者留言稱，晚上約7時50分，荃灣千色店附近發生斬人案，一名男子重傷，一人輕傷。警方表示，晚上7時許接獲一名男子報案，指其朋友遭一名持刀男子襲擊，胸口受傷。警員到場後，發現有兩名傷者，二人清醒分別送仁濟醫院及瑪嘉烈醫院。據悉，警方於事件中拘捕一人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180803/s00001/1533300612825?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180803%2Fs00001%2F1533300612825%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=STpkuu8aWteDIdWtpgo1KMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=9da2ed2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180803%2Fs00001%2F1533300612825%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=d94856a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180803/s00001/1533300612825?web_push=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e202456b8315dd47644422293b150ca759e8de5a","tid":766267,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"exact location係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749fbabce740ffaab3ceb4e9b5a3512293742a60","tid":766267,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"荃灣有市民於街頭被利刀刺傷，重傷送院。 今晚（8月3日）7時許，警方接報有人於荃灣大陂坊街被利刀刺傷，警員到場之後發現一名男子腹部中刀，血流不止，同時亦有一名男子胸口受輕傷。 救護員接報到場之後，將兩人送往仁濟醫院及瑪嘉烈醫院搶救。 消息指，隨後有一名男子到警署自首。 （香港突發事故報料區片段截圖）"},{"pid":"5ee35f76f09e20370bd413861a31a7c49fa997cb","tid":766267,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,